In the MATTER OF the Civil COMMITMENT OF S.M., SVP-308-03. (S.M. - Petitioner) C-1086 September Term 2018
082859 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 11, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002703-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
